spec_data.Name: mygui-tools
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the MyGUI tools, installed in /usr/lib64/MYGUI/Tools.
LayoutEditor is an application for designing UIs using MyGUI library,
FontEditor, ImageEditor and SkinEditor are also provided.
An helper script MyGUI-Tools is provided and installed in /usr/bin.
